headline: Is Coinbase Stock Justified After Acquisition Talks With BVNK and 53% Gain This Year?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Coinbase Global stock? You are not alone. In a world where crypto can move markets overnight, making sense of this industry trailblazer’s story is as much about reading the headlines as it is about reading the numbers.
